OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be cloudy with occasional light
OL,7,Frain. Then the rest of the night will
OL,8,Fremain cloudy with a little light rain
OL,9,Fat times.
OL,10,
OL,11,CThursday:FMainly dry with variable
OL,12,Famounts of cloud and just a few light
OL,13,Fshowers, these becoming more
OL,14,Fpersistent later in the afternoon.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FBreezy
OL,17,Fon Friday with occasional rain. Cloudy
OL,18,Fwith rain at first on Saturday, then
OL,19,Fdrier and eventually brighter in the
OL,20,Fafternoon. Dry with sunny spells on
OL,21,FSunday.
